Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:08.56,VIOLET_staff,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(350,100)}{\blur2}中翻:牧爾伯特少佐 自動翻譯人偶毛線 中校:愛を知らない雪梨 日聽:Ark 日校:燈 時軸:艾德曼銀製鍋 後期:冰喵 壓製:軍區司令cz
Comment: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,jp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ この依頼はカトレアに任せていいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:12.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あとは これか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「クトリガル国メナス基地」って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北部の元敵国じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな所から代筆の依頼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:26.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}基地にいる兵士からのドール需要は多いからね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:29.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各地に広告を出してるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:31.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何が問題なの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:35.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この国 最近内戦が起きてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わったはずの戦争を継続したい過激派と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穏健派が争ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:45.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まったく   せっかく平和になったっていうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:49.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世の中には戦争なしでは生きていけない人種もいるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:51.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メナス基地はその最前線だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙を書きたい気持ちも分かるが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さすがに危険すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも少し残念ね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:05.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦場にいる兵士も 伝えたいことがあるから ドールを呼んだんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:10.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが うちのドールたちを戦場にやるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:26.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:37.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我が隊はこれより出撃する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依頼の封筒が消えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それって確かキャンセルするって言ってた…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仕事があるって 今朝 出ていきましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確か クトリガルって言ってたし 片道1周間はかかりますね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しまった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなこと言われても無理ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから うちの配達区域じゃないんですって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騒がしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:14.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親方 この女の人が ここに自分を配達してほしいって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メナス基地だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しかも ライデンシャフトリヒから来ただと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうりで薄着なわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見な 嬢ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここがあんたが配達されたがってるメナス基地だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そしてここに収容所がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや… 「あった」かな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脱走ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}実際には外部からの手助けがあったみてえだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:44.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うちの国にも戦争を継続したい一派がいるんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そいつらが収容所にいたガルダリクの残党に武器を渡したせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:53.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦闘は泥沼化して 今や内戦状態だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:57.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メナス基地が最後の砦でギリギリ耐えちゃいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}周りは道路を遮断されてて支援に行けねえらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かったかい 嬢ちゃんが配達されてえ場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正真正銘の戦場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:12.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}けれど そんな所だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:16.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兵士には 誰かに伝えたい思いがあるのではないでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうは言っても 基地周辺にはアリ1匹近寄れねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ この山は標高も高く 徒歩で越えるのは困難です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:31.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なので どちらの軍も警戒していないはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:34.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}で… でも あの山を越えるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:39.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能です 飛行機と そして優秀なパイロットがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無理無理 いくらたどり着いても 上から落っことしでもしないかぎり…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}面白え嬢ちゃんだ 気に入ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうか 嬢ちゃんはドールかい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい お客様がお望みなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこでも駆けつけます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:11.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どんなものでもどこでも届けるのが郵便屋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なあ もうすぐ 大陸縦断鉄道が出来るんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:37.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ そしたら南の国まであっという間だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あっちの女の子はみんな可愛いっていうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うまい食い物もいっぱい届くようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:46.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい エール
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:53.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中隊長に伝令 第２小隊はこの地点より迂回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい 迂回します
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}配置予定時刻は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曹長 エール
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敵の待ち伏せだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}クソッ やってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伏せろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}クソッ クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダン…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願い 見捨てないで…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見捨てるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死にたくない 死にたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺だって死にたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イヤだ… エイダン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}置いてかないで…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エール エール
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イヤだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:38.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イヤだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死にたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は 帰るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帰るんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メナス基地も陥落してる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とても降りられるもんじゃねえ 帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ぜい弱だな カトリガル軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:54.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穏健派は腰抜けぞろいだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:59.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だからこそ 我々がもう一度率いてやる必要があるのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}では 狩を続けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛行機？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味方は飛んでないはずだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}子供？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺はあんたを知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデンシャフトリヒの少女兵なぜお前が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありませんが 下がっていただけますか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行くぞ 相手が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダン·フィールド様でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:18.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何で俺のこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お待たせしました 旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダンは遊ばないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ 金の使い道が思い浮かばなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だったらさ 故郷へ手紙でも送れば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙？ 戦場から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:54.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は手紙なんて生まれてこの方書いたことがないんだ 書き方なんて分からないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほら あのポスター
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:01.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ステキな女性が あなたの気持ちを手紙にしたためます」って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ エイダン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}せっかくだからキレイに撮ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少しの間 こちらで身を隠します
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝になれば 迎えが来る予定です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺 今熱いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}体を冷やさないためです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙 書いてくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今は手当てを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙 書きたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうすぐ死にそうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:05.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}キレイだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備できました 旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母さんと 父さんに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父さん 母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺のこと 今まで育ててくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙 書いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたの言葉を 私の指で覚えております
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これが最後の手紙になるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:43.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もし2人がまた生まれ変わって 夫婦になるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また俺を産んでほしい お願いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:56.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんなふうに 終わるはずじゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:03.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと幸せになって その姿を２人に見せるはず…だったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:09.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから 父さんと母さんも祈って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:15.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また俺を息子にしてよ お願いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:28.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんな言葉遣いで よかったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は このままのほうがいいと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:38.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君に そう言ってもらえると 何だか そんな気になる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:08.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様 他に手紙を送りたい方はいらっしゃいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア マリアに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア様 ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:24.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近所のさ 幼なじみなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小さい頃から一緒で 妹みたいだった人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:39.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告白されて 俺も多分好きで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:44.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも恋人らしいことなんて何もしないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}キスだってしたことないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様のその思いを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が手紙にします
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア 元気にしてるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:16.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚えているかな 俺に告白してくれた時のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:22.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は すごく…すごく すごく うれしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帰りたい 君の所に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死にたくないよ 帰りたい 君の所に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待ってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう目が開けられない ちゃんと書いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい 書いております
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット 俺の手紙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}助けてくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1人じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここにいます おそばにおります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願い…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手を握っておりますよ 旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だか寒くなってきた…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父さん 母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア キスして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫ですよ 旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙は 必ずお届けいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァンダル郵便社より
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:38.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}御社の荷物は無事回収した つつがなくそちらにお返しする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで いつ帰ってくるの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}えっと…ただし 1か所立ち寄り先があるとのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:50.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダンから手紙が来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:19.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こちらを エイダン·フィールド様より 預かってまいりました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウソよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:38.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダン…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エイダン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}息子を帰してくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ 私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:32.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:40.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守ってあげられなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死なせてしまって…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:03.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんなさい
Comment: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那這份委託就交給嘉德麗雅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:12.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還剩這份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}庫圖力高國梅納斯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這不是原來北部的敵對國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}從那種地方來的代筆委託？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:26.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因為基地裡的士兵對人偶的需求很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:29.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然廣告也發往了各地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:31.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:35.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這個國家 最近爆發了內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}激進派想把已經結束的戰爭再挑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為此與保守派展開了爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:45.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是的 明明好不容易才恢復了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:49.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界上還真有人離了戰爭活不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:51.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅納斯基地就是最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能理解他們想寫信的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是這也太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過挺可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:05.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}戰場上的士兵 一定是有話想說才來找人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:10.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是不能讓我們的人偶去戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:26.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:37.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}本隊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}委託的信封不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我記得那些是要取消的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}說是有工作 今天一大早就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我記得她說要去庫圖力高 單程要花一週吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算你這麼說也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都說了 那片不是我們的配送區域啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:14.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}師傅 這個女的說想把自己送去這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅納斯基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且還是從萊頓沙夫特里希來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怪不得穿這麼少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你來看 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這裡就是你想去的梅納斯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然後這裡有個收容所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 應該說曾經有過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是有人逃跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}據說實際上是有外部人員幫助他們逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:44.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們國家有一派人希望戰爭繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都怪他們把武器交給了收容所裡的加達里克殘黨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:53.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}戰鬥陷入膠著 現在處於內戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:57.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅納斯基地作為最後一座要塞還在勉強支撐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可周圍的道路似乎被阻斷了 援軍無法支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了嗎 你想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是真正的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:12.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:16.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那裡的士兵才會有話想告訴別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算你這麼說 可基地周圍連隻螞蟻都過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 這座山標高很高 很難徒步穿越
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:31.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以雙方應該都沒有設防
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:34.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是想翻過那座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:39.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}做得到 只要有飛機和優秀的飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒戲的 就算能飛到那裡 只要降落不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是有趣的小姑娘 我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原來小姑娘是人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 只要客人有要求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不論身在何處 都能為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:11.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不管人在哪裡 什麼東西都能送上門的才叫郵政局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}話說 縱貫大陸的鐵路就快竣工了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:37.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 這樣去南方的國家就很方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}聽說那邊的女生都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望還能多運點好吃的來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}南方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:46.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:53.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通知中隊長 第二小隊準備從這裡迂迴前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是 準備迂迴前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}預定到達時間是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}曹長 耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可惡 看我收拾你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}求求你 別丟下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎麼可能丟下你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們要活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想死 不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要…艾丹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}別丟下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}耶爾 耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:38.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅納斯基地也淪陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}降落不了了 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}庫圖力高軍真是不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:54.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}保守派就是群窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:59.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以需要我們重新領導他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我們繼續狩獵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}飛機？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友軍怎麼可能飛來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}動手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}萊頓沙夫特里希的少女兵 為什麼你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉 可以請你們撤退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}走 選錯對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請問是艾丹·菲爾德大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:18.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你怎麼認識我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}讓您久等了 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹不去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 想不到該怎麼花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就給老家寫信如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}信？從戰場寄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:54.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我從來沒寫過信 也不知道該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你看那張海報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:01.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「由出色的女性將您的心意化為書信」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}吶 艾丹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}難得一次 把我拍好看些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們暫時藏身在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等天亮後 會有人來接的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我現在很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是為了防止身體降溫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能幫我寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}現在還是療傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我應該快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:05.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}準備好了 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}寫給媽媽和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你們把我養大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您說的話 我用手指記下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這可能是我最後一封信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:43.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}假如你們有來生 又再結為夫妻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望能再把我生下來 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:56.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}本不該這樣結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:03.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}應該活得更幸福 讓你們看到我幸福的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:09.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以 爸爸媽媽也祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:15.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望我還能當你們的兒子 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:28.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這麼說好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我覺得這麼說就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:38.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}聽你這麼說 我覺得這樣也挺好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:08.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爺 您還想寫信給別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞 寫給瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞大人 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:24.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她是住在我家附近的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們自幼就在一起 像我妹妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:39.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她向我表白 我大概也喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:44.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我們還沒嘗試過戀人間會做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}連親都沒親過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爺的這份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我會寫成信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:16.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還記得嗎 你向我告白的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:22.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我非常…非常非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想回到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想死 想回到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}眼睛睜不開了 都寫下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 我的信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你救下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我就在這裡 就在您身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我握住您的手了 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感覺變冷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞 親一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已經
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事了 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一定會把信送到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}班達爾郵政公司來消息說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:38.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}貴公司的貨物已順利回收 將平安送回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那她什麼時候回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我看看…但需繞行一處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:50.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:19.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是艾丹·菲爾德大人交給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:38.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾丹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你把兒子送回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:32.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不…
