Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我沒能保護好他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對不起
