Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:42.65,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一隻小鳥 婉轉鳴叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:53.71,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四處尋找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:59.53,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在溫柔編織出的搖籃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:05.17,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}向著明天前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:11.20,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}不論天晴 不論風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:15.89,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}只為能守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:26.80,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}獨一無二的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:37.62,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}無名之花 靜靜地沉眠
